column5: Looks like a great board looking forward to sharing some stories and pics and looking forward to hearing yours. 10

Welcome to our OFC family 10 pointer.  I'm going to assume you're a hunter as well as an angler with a handle like that.  Enjoy the board and don't forget, .....we like pictures.
I am a hunter as well, I love fishing for Bass, Muskie, Pike, Walleye, trout, etc.  Thanks
